  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! w (. shape :width))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. canvas :path
     [[:M (+ l (* w 0.17)) b]
      [:A (* w 0.14) (* h 0.25) 0 0 1 (+ l (* w 0.22)) (+ t (* h 0.31))]
      [:A (* w 0.14) (* h 0.2) 0 0 1 (+ l (* w 0.76)) (+ t (* h 0.48))]
      [:A (* w 0.16) (* h 0.25) 0 0 1 (+ l (* w 0.87)) b]
      [:Z]] seed)
  (. shape :renderText canvas))

  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! w (. shape :width))
  (def! xc (/ (+ l r) 2))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. canvas :ellipse (- xc (* w 0.27)) t (+ xc (* w 0.27)) (+ t (* h 0.35)) seed)
  (. canvas :path
     [[:M l b]
      [:C l (+ t (* h 0.2)) r (+ t (* h 0.2)) r b]
      [:Z]] seed)

scripts.script:
(do
  (def! checked (. shape :getPropertyValue "Checked"))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! l (if checked (- (. shape :right) h) (. shape :left)))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! m 2)
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (if checked (. canvas :setFillColor (. shape :strokeColor)))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :setFillColor (. shape :fillColor))
  (. canvas :ellipse (+ l m) (+ t m) (+ l (- h m)) (- b m) seed))

scripts.script:
(do
  (def! c (. shape :getCenter))

  (def! x (nth c 0))
  (def! y (nth c 1))
  (def! r (/ w 2))

  (if (= o "right") (. canvas :arc x y r 90 270 seed)))

      [:L r (+ t m2)]
